

= Derivatives & Hedging Analyst (Superannuation Fund) - Career Pathways

This document outlines career progression for derivatives and hedging roles within major superannuation funds in Australia. These professionals manage the fund's use of derivatives for portfolio hedging, risk management, and tactical positioning across global markets.

